videos.description: After a steal by Temple's Alani Moore II, Jalen Adams sprints back on defense to deny Moore's layup attempt.
videos.headline: Connecticut's Adams rejects Temple's fast-break layup attempt

videos.description: After a Temple steal, Shizz Alston Jr. takes it down to opposing territory and tosses it up to Quinton Rose who slams down the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Temple steal leads to electrifying alley-oop

videos.description: After a Nate Pierre-Louis defensive steal,  Pierre-Louis takes it down the court and springs up for the Temple dunk.
videos.headline: Pierre-Louis gets up for fast break Temple dunk

videos.description: After an errant UConn pass, Quinton Rose plays the ball up the court to Shizz Alston Jr. who puts the moves on two Huskies defenders for the nifty layup.
videos.headline: Temple's Alston Jr. schools two UConn defenders

videos.description: Temple's Obi Enechionyia drives toward the basket then dishes it off to Ernest Aflakpui who gets fouled while powering over 2 UConn defenders for the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Aflakpui wins in the post to extend the Owls' lead

videos.description: During a stoppage in play, a Temple fan competes in a half-court shot competition to win a 1-year lease on a car and drains the shot.
videos.headline: Lucky Temple fan drains a half-court shot
